{"tid":2462888,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"酒店房變毒品包裝工場 廚師以搵快錢利誘兩中學生販毒被捕","createTime":"2021-03-26T09:32:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T09:39:51.000Z","uid":44209,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0d1fbf77cf94a74461d3c8775303cf904090528a","tid":2462888,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T09:32:05.000Z","msg":"咁撚白痴都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方昨日（25日）在荃灣區以涉嫌「販毒」拘捕3名介乎15至22歲的本地男子，現被扣留調查，行動中檢獲的毒品市值約40,200元，經調查後相信有不法之徒利用青年「搵快錢」的心態，指使他們包裝及販賣毒品。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，新界南總區機動部隊在昨日凌晨2時30分於荃灣區進行反罪惡巡邏，其間在禾笛街附近截查一名16歲、正就讀中四的姓胡青年。<br />\n<br />\n當時該青年未能出示任何身份證明文件，但身上有一張區內酒店的房卡，<strong><span class=\"red\">他向警員聲稱身份證明文件遺漏在酒店房內，警員於是和他一起返回酒店</span></strong>，並在職員協助下進入酒店房間作出調查。<br />\n<br />\n全文："},{"pid":"10f8f949fbd1ed69a41e3c33f281f1ac847cb259","tid":2462888,"uid":44209,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T09:32:35.000Z","msg":"求救，弟弟無辜被告藏毒！弟弟竟然認罪！<br />\n<br />\n希望有人能幫我，現留下telegram: <br />\n@hugo19911"},{"pid":"155a108f3dc5ba1d2ab9ef95530e730a6b3ee1a5","tid":2462888,"uid":374602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10f8f949fbd1ed69a41e3c33f281f1ac847cb259","tid":2462888,"uid":44209,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T09:32:35.000Z","msg":"求救，弟弟無辜被告藏毒！弟弟竟然認罪！<br />\n<br />\n希望有人能幫我，現留下telegram: <br />\n@hugo19911"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T09:33:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f80532e1baf3dab488a2f70e57d7e18a08e25e2b","tid":2462888,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T09:34:19.000Z","msg":"咁拉唔拉到個廚?"},{"pid":"f57e0bff99e6b362b09716ec84a40b9717f3359c","tid":2462888,"uid":44209,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T09:34:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210326/RQXPQ6HTG5G35I6SBLTDKWOS3Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link